data.description: B-E-A-U-T-I-F-U-L Waterfront Home Waiting for YOU To Come Make Memories and Enjoy Nature’s Tranquility!!! Featuring Amazing Lake Views on All Levels of The House, As Well As the Two-Tiered Deck!!! YOU Will Be Proud to Welcome Guests All Seasons of The Year, Summer BBQs, Fourth of July Parties, Enjoy the Fall Foliage with Friends, Watch the Spring Flowers Bloom, and Enjoy Your Morning Coffee While Watching the Sunrise and Hearing The Lake Thaw in The Winter!!! Architecturally Designed for Families of All Sizes, YOU Will Be Thoroughly Impressed with The Use of Square Footage All Throughout the Home, LARGE Walk-In Master Closet, TONS of Storage Space, Large Jack N Jill Bathroom, the List Goes On and On and ON!!! All Appliances  Convey with The Property (INCLUDING REFRIDGERATOR, WASHER & DRYER), It Is Simply Waiting for YOU To Come Make It YOUR Own Private Oasis!!!
